# Todolist

Repository maintainers record planned implementation work in this directory.

Use `NNNN-slug.md` with `Status: Planned|In-Progress|Done` and one executable
`Verify:` command. Move to Done only after that command passes.

Run `bin/aicoding.exe todolist --json` for the deterministic queue view.

Authority: [AiCoding todolist contract](https://github.com/JiaxI2/AiCoding/blob/main/docs/todolist/README.md).
